			<div class="text-col">
				<p class="tag tag--brand">Buying & Selling Property</p>
				<h2 class="heading heading--brand">Buying or selling property in Kilkenny?</h2>
				<p class="body body--brand">We manage the full conveyancing process from first instruction to completion — contracts reviewed, title investigated, mortgage requirements handled throughout.</p>
				<ul class="points points--brand">
					<li>Contracts reviewed before you sign</li>
					<li>Title checks and compliance handled</li>
					<li>Mortgage requirements managed</li>
					<li>Completion coordinated throughout</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/services/buying-and-selling-property" class="btn-outline-light">Our property service</a>
			</div>
			<div class="img-frame img-frame--amber-outline img-frame--sm">
				<Image src={propertyImage} alt="" width={500} height={600} class="img-fill" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

